name: Paradise III by Martiosza
description: Collaboration with Marta Gliwinska - Limited Edition of 100 pieces. I am a quality plastic watch, with MIYOTA stainless quartz cassette mechanism and stainless steel metal bottom cover. My strap is made of white silicone and has a metal buckle. Pshhht… the battery will also come with me! My size: case diameter: 35 mm; total length: 25,5 cm
